  "title": "Head of Department (Finance&admin)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Reporting directly to the senior management, he/she will work closely with the senior management to ensure smooth running of all operational/administrative aspects of the center, including human resource, administrative and legal management.     </li><li>Monitor and review divisional performance throughout the year to achieverevenue and growth KPIs. Identify and implement solutions to address performance gaps when financial or operational indicators deviate from budgeter targets.</li><li>Develop and implement operational policies, long and short term planning initiatives in accordance with company's objectives to drive revenue growth.</li><li>Establish budgets, forecast, and general operating procedures and monitor cost control procedures. Engage and responsible for monthly financial reporting to senior management.</li><li>Uphold and foster the organization’s culture, mission, vision, and values across all departments.</li><li>Liaise with China HQ on reporting, approval, and compliance matters.</li><li>Lead and guide the HR, Administration, and Legal teams in alignment with organizational goals.</li><li>Handle any other work assigned by the senior management.</li></ul>",
